    <summary>A free lightweight 8-bit voxel editor and interactive path tracing renderer.</summary>
    <description>
## Features
* Selection Tool, Frame Based Animation
* Emissive Area Lighting, Fog, Scattering
* Transparent voxels with Refraction and Attenuation
* Voxel Shader, Marching Cube Export

## Package parameters
- `/user` - Install in user profile's folder(C:\Users\user\AppData\Roaming\magicavoxel) instead of allusers(administrator) folder(C:\ProgramData\chocolatey\lib\magicavoxel\tools\MagicaVoxel-version-win64).

Example: choco install magicavoxel --params "/user"

magicavoxel in user profile's folder will not get uninstalled automatically by this package. Please remove magicavoxel manually after choco uninstall magicavoxel.

## Notes
If you saved your voxel art at allusers(administrator) magicavoxel folder(needs admin permission). The folder path is here.
C:\ProgramData\chocolatey\lib\magicavoxel\tools\"previous-version-number"\vox (or \export folder)

I recommend use your home folder instead of above.
choco upgrade will not delete the previous version magicavoxel folder, but choco uninstall will delete all magicavoxel folder.

64bit only from 0.99.6.4 version.
    </description>
